
** Latin-9 under GNU/Linux

  - local-fontpath.sh
  - M-x *l9* (de DE@euro)
  - M-x *iln9* neue Deutsche Sprache
  - M-x *ild9* alte Deutsche Sprache

** Latin-1 under GNU/Linux

  - M-x *l1* (de DE)
  - M-x *iln* neue Deutsche Sprache
  - M-x *ild* alte Deutsche Sprache

** ispell-complete-word

  - makes completions from the file ispell-complete-word-dict.

** flyspell

  - *flyspell-prog-mode* use this mode in programming languages. It's
    enabled by *c-mode, emacs-lisp-mode, cperl-mode and sh-mode*.

